TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content:
Here let me fix that *gets giant flame fun and shoots troll.

Waiter, why are you in my soup?

HELP! I CANT GET OUT!

Waiter, there is an universe in my soup!

Just be glad you got a bowl that big for just 9 dollars.

Waiter there is soap in my soup!

That's our pun soup, sir. That was a punny one, right? [loud booing is heard around the restaurant]

Waiter! There's a...wait, what the heck is that? Is that...a bar of gold? Wait, no, I found it!

*pulls revolver out*

Sorry to say, but that's mine.

Waiter, my soupgame has been rigged the whole time!

I like the word rig. Riiiiig. Sorry, what did you say?

Waiter, there is a scamming video game developer in my soup sending me emails!

Just spray him with more soup !

Waiter ! There is an

in my soup !

Be glad.

Waiter get yourself out of my soup.

NEVER!

Waiter! There is a guy in mah soup!

Oh, sorry, that's our Soylent Kerb soup.

Waiter! There's a o_O in my soup!

No that's just two mushrooms and some spice.

Waiter get your tie out of my soup

Edited October 16, 2014 by LABHOUSE

I don't wear ties, sir.

Waiter, there's a bog in my soup, with a tiny person walking around in it!

And it has muddy rubber boots on? Then it's probably Sun again. If you give it a muddy lake, chances are it will get out of your soup.

WAITER! Elysium is in my soup!

Too bad all the humans inside of Elysium are already boiled, I guess.

Waiter, there's a notepad in my soup!

It reads "The money is hid at..." YOU NEVER HEARD ME SAY THAT!

Waiter, there's a dadaist exestentialist in my soup.

You did what to what?

Waiter! There's a brick in my soup!

When you see it, you'll drink bricks.

Waiter! I asked for the Halloween Special Soup! Not the Christmas Special!

Don't worry, both of them are spooky.

Waiter, there's a video clip in my soup!

wait1!!1 its proff of teh illuminiti!!!1! woah it ses dat shrek is illuminate! omg 30000000000000spooky5000000000000me11!

Waiter! There's RCS in my soup!

The reaction control system is controlling my reaction.

Waiter, there's a pie in my soup!

Waiter: What flavor is it?

Me: Pie Flavor [epic intro music]

Waiter, my foot is in my soup!

Why you impudent son of a gun! *waiter kicks Starwhip out from the restaurant*

Waiter, now Starwhip's foot is in my soup! >:-[

No.

Waiter, there's a very muddy peat bog in my soup!

You like it, though.

Waiter, Sun cannot decide if he is a Sun or Mud!

Why not both?

Waiter! There's a 40mm grenade in my soup!
